description:
CelcomDigi App – Built for you, around you
 
We are phasing out the MyDigi and Celcom Life apps by 31st December 2025. The CelcomDigi App is here to take their place, designed around what matters most to you: convenience, safety, and a little more delight every day.
 
Everyday tasks, made easy
* Everything in one app. Prepaid, postpaid, fibre, home wireless, even your family’s and supplementary lines, all managed in one place
* Check your internet usage at a glance
* View your full transaction history
* Pay bills in seconds
* Auto Reload Magic so you never run out of credit
* Pre-Book Roaming before you fly so you connect the moment you land
 
We take your safety seriously
* eKYC verification
* Linked device protection
* Biometric login and SSO
 
Everything else built in
* Stay entertained with Disney+ & more
* Travel smarter with roaming you set up in advance
* Keep your phone safe with the CD Safety Page, a dedicated hub with solutions and tips
 
Rewards you’ll love
* Vouchers, promos, and perks
 
For You – An app that understands your needs
* Smarter recommendations. From data passes to roaming deals, the app learns your habits and suggests what you’ll actually need
* Exclusive offers. Promos and bundles tailored to your lifestyle, not just generic deals
* Always relevant. The more you use the app, the more it adapts to bring you what matters most
 
Your daily dose of fun
* Daily Streak check-ins that unlock rewards
* 3-2-1 Weekly Surprise, every Wednesday at 3:21 PM
* Secret Surprise: Psst, Hidden freebies in the app
 
Something more
* Help That’s Always On with AI-powered support, instant answers any time of day
 
Why download?
With the CelcomDigi App, you can:
* Stay in control of usage, payments, and history
* Manage all your CelcomDigi services in one place
* Access entertainment, lifestyle, and protection services with ease
* Feel safe with security built into every layer
* Enjoy personalised offers and little surprises, every day
 
Download the CelcomDigi app and be ready for what’s coming soon!

The Google app keeps you in the know about things that matter to you. Find quick answers, explore your interests and stay up to date with Discover.

• Use your camera to identify what you're looking at – whether that's a colourful butterfly, a spiky plant or anything else you're curious about.
• Translate over 100 languages on things like street signs, menus and any other words you can point your camera at.
• See something you like? Use your camera to find out where you can buy it.
• Refine your camera searches by adding words – whether you want those shoes but in 'blue', or want to learn how to 'repair' that broken piece on your bicycle.
• Search by singing, even when you've forgotten the lyrics. Hum a song into the Google app to find out what it is.
• Use your camera for homework help. With step-by-step guides and videos, you can learn ways to solve maths, chemistry, biology and physics problems.


Get personalised updates in Discover:
• Stay in the know about topics that interest you.
• Start your morning with weather and top news.
• Get real-time updates on sports, films and events.
• Know as soon as your favourite artists drop new albums.
• Get stories about your interests and hobbies.
• Follow interesting topics, straight from Search results.


Search safely and securely:
• All searches in the Google app are protected by encrypting the connection between your device and Google.
• Privacy controls are easy to find and use. Tap your profile picture to access your menu and delete recent search history from your account with one click.
• Search takes a proactive approach to filtering webspam to help ensure that you see safe, high-quality results.


More ways to access Google:
• Google Search widget — search from your home screen or lock screen with the new Google widget. Choose from two widgets, giving you a quick access search bar in both sizes, and other search shortcuts to choose from such as Lens, Voice and Incognito in the medium-sized widget.


Learn more about what the Google app can do for you: http://www.google.com/search/about

Privacy policy: https://www.google.com/policies/privacy

Digi Telecommunications Sdn. Bhd. Malaysia has launched the new MyDigi Telco App, which provides Digi users with a streamlined, all-in-one experience. For prepaid and postpaid phone plans, MyDigi Mobile App is a smarter way to manage your Digi mobile account. By using the quick link buttons, you can pay and manage your phone bills, check internet usage & coverage, top up your internet data, make subscriptions and more! It is basically your personalised data manager and billing app!
Data Manager & Billing App: Pay & Check Mobile Bills and Top Up Prepaid Credit
Pay your prepaid or postpaid mobile bills hassle-free, without having to go to the Digi store with the MyDigi app. You can pay your bills with only a few clicks, no matter where you are.
Download past and current billing statements of your phone plan to monitor and keep track of your mobile bills. 
Do you have a shortage of prepaid credits? Is your prepaid phone plan about to expire? To keep in touch with your loved ones, simply reload or topup your phone credit with the MyDigi app. 
Depending on the quantity of online prepaid reload you buy, you'll get more Internet data, call time, and credits. 

Check Internet Usage, Network Signal & Coverage, & Switch Internet Package
Check your internet usage, access and coverage, located under the “Internet” section, as displayed on the homescreen. The data quota and data usage are displayed side by side to give you a clear picture of how much Internet data you consume and how much you need. You can also use it to check the areas that can give you the best network signal.
Digi users can also view how many days remain till their phone plan or Digi postpaid data quota expires or is renewed for the next use cycle. 
If you wish to check your other numbers' mobile data usage, go to the side menu, choose your phone number, and the usage information for that number will be displayed. 
When your current prepaid or postpaid data package expires, you can switch to a new one using the MyDigi app!
Internet Top Up and International Roaming Passes:
Is your mobile data plan insufficient? You can buy Internet add-ons that are suitable for your usage and budget. 
The add ons range from basic Internet access to more intensive entertainment (games, music, and videos), as well as larger data purchase options for general use. 
The 'Buy Add-Ons' tab on the homescreen or the 'Box of Surprise' page in the app can be used to purchase add-ons. 
Simply select the country to which you will be traveling before subscribing to a roaming Internet package.
Once you have made the purchase, using it as a hotspot for your other devices or gadgets will be easy. 

Support Section
Under the “Support” section, users can find the available FAQs under the "Self Help" common questions should the need arise.
If you cannot find the answers you need, you can navigate to the "Get In Touch" section to raise a ticket to MyDigi's agent for any inquiries.
You can even check the status of your ticket raised under “My Case Status”.

Digi Fibre Home & Broadband Internet Connection 
Unlimited High Speed Fibre Home Internet Broadband Plan, paired with our amazing WiFi router!
Malaysia's best value fiberhome broadband plan. Access your fiber internet and broadband connection data usage, internet consumption and pay bills using MyDigi App. 
Sign up now to get a FREE WiFi router, enjoy unlimited Internet & savings with Digi!

Digi EKYC App: Self-Registration and SIM Card Verification/Activation (Prepaid & Postpaid) 
With the Digi App’s Electronic Know Your Customer (EKYC) feature, it’s easy to activate your prepaid or postpaid SIM card. Just tap on ‘Activate SIM’ to begin. Now, everyone can enjoy Digi’s excellent coverage and fast data plans!
To learn more about the MyDigi app, simply log on to https://www.digi.com.my/mydigi-app or https://www.digi.com.my/support/help-center/mydigi-app/box-surprise to access specific topics on the MyDigi app. Enjoy an all-new app experience on MyDigi today!

Explore the world smarter with Travel Camera & Compass – your ultimate travel companion!
Whether you’re wandering through ancient cities or hiking remote trails, our app combines powerful tools to help you capture, navigate, and experience the world like never before.

Key Features: 
- Travel Camera: Take stunning photos wherever you go with our optimized travel camera. Every snapshot can be automatically tagged with your location, so you’ll always remember where each memory was made. Plus, choose from a wide range of beautiful styles and filters to make your travel photos stand out – from cinematic tones to vibrant holiday vibes. Perfect for quick snapshots, scenic landscapes, and share-worthy moments..

- Interactive Map with Travel Highlights: Discover new destinations through an immersive world map. We’ve marked iconic landmarks, hidden gems, and trending spots directly on the map. You can view different terrain types – satellite, hybrid, or standard – for a customized navigation experience.

- 3D Globe View: Zoom out and explore the Earth in 3D! A global view helps you visualize your travel path and highlights locations worth visiting.

- Watch Travel Highlight Videos: Get a real feel of places before you go. Watch curated or live video clips from various destinations worldwide, giving you a preview of the adventure that awaits.

- Extract Audio from Videos: Want to save the sound from your favorite travel clips? With just a tap, you can convert any video into an audio file. Great for saving local music, soundscapes, or memorable voice notes.

- Digital Compass: Navigate confidently, even when offline. The built-in compass shows your current direction and bearing – essential for hikers, trekkers, or road trippers.

Why Choose Travel Camera & Compass?

* Combines multiple travel tools in one app
* Helps you discover and plan your next destination
* Enhances your travel experience through rich media
* Intuitive interface designed for travelers of all kinds
* Lightweight and battery-friendly, perfect for long trips

Whether you’re a backpacker, travel vlogger, or casual explorer, Travel Camera & Compass gives you everything you need to document your journey and stay oriented wherever you are.

Travel Camera is your smart travel companion, allowing you to capture, organize, and share beautiful memories from your journeys with ease.

- Free up storage instantly with one tap.

 No accidental deletions, no surprises — you're always in control.

Your privacy is fully protected — even we can’t access your photos.





Payment & Subscription Terms:


Choose between the following subscription options for unlimited access to all features:


• Weekly Subscription
• Lifetime Subscription


FREE TRIAL FOR 7 DAYS - OFFERING UNLIMITED GALLERY CLEANING FOR A LIMITED TIME


***You may cancel your subscription at any time***


Cleanup’s free trial allows you unlimited access to all features for the duration of 7 days. Your account will be automatically charged for renewal, based on the annual subscription plan, within 24 hours before the end of the 7 days free trial period.


You can cancel auto-renewal at any time, given that the cancellation is at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when making a purchase of an auto-renewing subscription.


***Manage your subscription directly from your iPhone***
Subscriptions can be managed by the user and auto-renewal can be turned off by going to the Account Settings:
- Open the Settings app.
- Tap your name.
- Tap Subscriptions.
- Tap the subscription that you want to manage.

Google Authenticator adds an extra layer of security to your online accounts by adding a second step of verification when you sign in. This means that in addition to your password, you'll also need to enter a code that is generated by the Google Authenticator app on your phone.
